===Ships attacked===
{{GeoGroupTemplate}}
During his career Lüth sank 46 commercial ships for {{GRT|225,204}}, one warship of {{convert|552|LT}}, and damaged two ships for {{GRT|17,343}}.<ref name=Helgason/> His last patrol saw {{GS|U-181||2}} at sea for 206 days, patrolling the waters between [[Cape Town]] and [[Madagascar]], second only to [[Eitel-Friedrich Kentrat]]'s voyage in {{GS|U-196||2}} .{{sfn|Blair|2000b|p=305}}

